name: James Cameron
bio: James Cameron is a Canadian filmmaker known for directing Titanic and Avatar.

name: Frank Darabont
bio: Frank Darabont is an American director best known for The Shawshank Redemption and The Green Mile.

name: Lana Wachowski
bio: Lana Wachowski is an American filmmaker, one of the directors behind The Matrix trilogy.

name: Lilly Wachowski
bio: Lilly Wachowski is an American filmmaker, known for directing The Matrix alongside her sister Lana.

name: Robert Zemeckis
bio: Robert Zemeckis is an American director famous for films such as Back to the Future and Forrest Gump.

name: Christopher Nolan
bio: Christopher Nolan is a British-American filmmaker known for mind-bending movies such as Inception and The Dark Knight trilogy.
